email_content:
Hi Sarah,

I hope you’re doing well! I wanted to share a quick update on our most recent admissions cycle:

• Applications rose noticeably, making this one of our most competitive years so far.
• We admitted a smaller percentage of applicants, reflecting the heightened selectivity.
• The incoming class boasts very strong academic profiles and represents students from dozens of countries, giving us our most globally diverse cohort to date.

Everyone here is excited about the energy and perspectives this group will bring to campus.

Let me know if you’d like any additional details. Always happy to keep you in the loop.

Best regards,
[Your Name]
